       Name: Assertion Form
       Kind: Spell
     Target: TAR_CHAR_SELF
   Position: POS_STANDING
   Min Mana: 60
 Wait Beats: 24
 Can Learn: FALSE
Noun Damage: None
   Wear-Off: Your assertion form fades.
Acquisition:
   - Psionicist: level 60
Description:
   Assertion Form is an advanced psionic self-enhancement technique. The
   Psionicist enters a formalized combat trance, overlaying their normal
   consciousness with a highly structured mental combat framework. In this
   state, their perception sharpens, their reflexes are guided by predictive
   psionic modeling, and they fight with unusual precision and efficiency.

   While Assertion Form is active, the Psionicist gains bonuses to their
   combat stats — improved attack, damage, and defense — reflecting the
   enhanced mental engagement with every action. The form is difficult to
   maintain under severe stress, and particularly powerful disruptions may
   cause it to collapse. It is the Psionicist's equivalent of a martial
   combat trance, achieved through mental rather than physical discipline.
